| **Cultural Conflict**          | Opinions shaped by cultural identities, stereotypes, and social group membership                   | Strong predictor of support; linked to negative stereotypes of gun owners ([Kleck et al., 2009](https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S0047235209000932)) |
